gin.com/google-fonts-univers/\">Google Fonts Similar to Univers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"arthur\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5522:\"<p>Released in 1957, Univers is a sans-serif font designed by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrian_Frutiger\">Adrian Frutiger</a> and released by his employer <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deberny_%26_Peignot\">Deberny &amp; Peignot</a>. One of the most recognisable uses of Univers is the eBay logo.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo-1024x447.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2655\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo-1024x447.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo-300x131.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo-768x335.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo-640x279.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/ebay-logo.png 1100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure><p>To use Univers on your website you will need a Webfont license. At $299 per 250,000 page views, it’s one of the more expensive fonts. Luckily we have found some similar fonts available from Google Fonts that are free to use.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost-1024x270.png\" alt=\"Univers Font Cost\" class=\"wp-image-2656\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost-1024x270.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost-300x79.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost-768x203.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost-640x169.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-font-cost.png 1416w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>https://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/univers</figcaption></figure><h3>Google Fonts Alternatives</h3><p>Univers is an excellent font that has stood the test of time. Here are four fonts with a very similar aesthetic:</p><h4>Open Sans</h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans.png\" alt=\"Univers Comparison with Open Sans\" class=\"wp-image-2749\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans.png 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans-300x164.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans-768x420.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans-1024x560.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-open-sans-640x350.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Open Sans Comparison</figcaption></figure><h4>Roboto</h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto.png\" alt=\"Univers Comparison with Roboto\" class=\"wp-image-2750\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto.png 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto-300x164.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto-768x420.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto-1024x560.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-roboto-640x350.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Roboto Comparison</figcaption></figure><h3>Other Alternatives</h3><p>The next two suggestions are <a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/web-safe-system-fonts/\">Web Safe Fonts</a>, which means they don&#8217;t rely on the Google Fonts API and will generally load faster.</p><h4><a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-similar-futura/\">Futura</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura.png\" alt=\"Univers Comparison with Futura\" class=\"wp-image-2752\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura.png 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura-300x164.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura-768x420.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura-1024x560.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/univers-alternative-futura-640x350.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Futura Comparison</figcaption></figure><h4><a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-helvetica-neue/\">Helvetica Neue</a></h4><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue-1024x560.png\" alt=\"Univers Comparison with Helvetica Neue\" class=\"wp-image-2753\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue-1024x560.png 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue-300x164.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue-768x420.png 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue-640x350.png 640w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/futura-alternative-helvetica-neue.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Helvetica Neue Comparison</figcaption></figure><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-univers/\">Google Fonts Similar to Univers</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-univers/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"          \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Are Google Fonts Free for Commercial Use?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 29 May 2019 09:40:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Uncategorized\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://fontsplugin.com/?p=380\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:750:\"<p>The simple answer is yes, all the fonts included in the Google Fonts library are released under licenses that allow you to use them for free, in both commercial and personal applications. The open source fonts in the Google Fonts catalog are published under licenses that allow you to use them on any website, whether&#8230; <a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"Are Google Fonts Free for Commercial Use?\"</span></a> &#8594;</p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/\">Are Google Fonts Free for Commercial Use?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"arthur\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2818:\"<p>The simple answer is yes, all the fonts included in the Google Fonts library are released under licenses that allow you to use them for free, in both commercial and personal applications.</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The open source fonts in the Google Fonts catalog are published under licenses that allow you to use them on any website, whether it’s commercial or personal.&nbsp;</p><cite><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq\">https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq</a></cite></blockquote><p>More specifically, the fonts use one of three license types:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://opensource.org/licenses/OFL-1.1\">SIL OPEN FONT LICENSE 1.1</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.apache.org/licenses/\">Apache License</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ubuntu.com/legal/font-licence\">UBUNTU FONT LICENCE</a></li></ul><p>All three licenses place very little restrictions on how you can use the fonts. The primary restrictions are based around redistribution.</p><p>A key requirement is that if you distribute the fonts, you must also include the original license files.</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>You must give any other recipients of the Work or Derivative Works a copy of this License; and</p><p>You must cause any modified files to carry prominent notices stating that You changed the files; and</p><p>You must retain, in the Source form of any Derivative Works that You distribute, all copyright, patent, trademark, and attribution notices from the Source form of the Work, excluding those notices that do not pertain to any part of the Derivative Works; and</p><cite><a href=\"http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0\">http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0</a></cite></blockquote><p>It&#8217;s also important to not distribute modified versions using the original name:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The Original Version must retain its name, unmodified.<br>Modified Versions which are Substantially Changed must be renamed to avoid use of the name of the Original Version or similar names entirely.</p><cite><a href=\"https://www.ubuntu.com/legal/font-licence\">https://www.ubuntu.com/legal/font-licence</a></cite></blockquote><p>Lastly, the OPEN FONT LICENSE prohibits selling the fonts by themselves:</p><blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>1) Neither the Font Software nor any of its individual components, in Original or Modified Versions, may be sold by itself.</p><cite><a href=\"https://github.com/google/fonts/blob/master/ofl/abeezee/OFL.txt\">https://github.com/google/fonts/blob/master/ofl/abeezee/OFL.txt</a></cite></blockquote><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/\">Are Google Fonts Free for Commercial Use?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://fontsplugin.com/google-fonts-commercial-use/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"          \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Baskerville Font\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 28 May 2019 12:38:55 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Uncategorized\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://fontsplugin.com/?p=2503\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:693:\"<p>Baskerville is one of the oldest fonts we have covered, it was designed in the 1750s by John Baskerville. Variants of the font are still included in both Windows and macOS operating systems to this day and it&#8217;s considered to be a web-safe font. Microsoft Windows The variant included in Windows is named &#8216;Baskerville Old&#8230; <a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> \"Baskerville Font\"</span></a> &#8594;</p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/\">Baskerville Font</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"arthur\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3591:\"<p>Baskerville is one of the oldest fonts we have covered, it was designed in the 1750s by John Baskerville. Variants of the font are still included in both Windows and macOS operating systems to this day and it&#8217;s considered to be a <a href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/web-safe-system-fonts/\">web-safe font</a>.</p><h4>Microsoft Windows</h4><p>The variant included in Windows is named &#8216;Baskerville Old Face&#8217; and was released in 1992 by designer Isaac Moore.</p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-old-face.png\" alt=\"Baskerville Old Face\" class=\"wp-image-2729\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-old-face.png 500w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-old-face-300x32.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><figcaption>Baskerville Old Face</figcaption></figure></div><h4>Apple macOS</h4><p>macOS includes a font simply named &#8216;Baskerville&#8217;, this is a 1923 revival of the original Baskerville typeface by the Monotype Design Studio.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos.jpg\" alt=\"Baskerville Font\" class=\"wp-image-2730\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos.jpg 1280w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos-300x92.jpg 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos-768x235.jpg 768w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos-1024x314.jpg 1024w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/baskerville-font-macos-640x196.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /><figcaption>Baskerville</figcaption></figure><h4>Kate Spade Logo</h4><p>The Kate Space logo is designed using another variation of the original Baskerville typeface named &#8216;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.myfonts.com/fonts/itc/new-baskerville/\" target=\"_blank\">ITC New Baskerville Roman</a>&#8216;.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville.png\" alt=\"kate space logo baskerville\" class=\"wp-image-2658\" srcset=\"https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville.png 621w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville-150x150.png 150w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville-300x300.png 300w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville-128x128.png 128w, https://fontsplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/kate-spade-logo-baskerville-256x256.png 256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\" /><figcaption>Kate Spade Logo</figcaption></figure><h3>Using Baskerville on Your Website</h3><p>Baskerville is not very popular on the web, that&#8217;s likely down to it&#8217;s very traditional aesthetic. A lot of websites that use a serif-typeface instead opt for the more modern-looking Georgia.</p><p>As it&#8217;s a web-safe font you can use it on your website by simply adding it to the CSS code:</p><pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>body {\n  font-family: Baskerville, Baskerville Old Face, Hoefler Text, Garamond, Times New Roman, serif; \n}</code></pre><p class=\"note\">Note: Due to the different naming conventions across operating systems, we have to include multiple fallback fonts.</p><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/\">Baskerville Font</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://fontsplugin.com\">Fonts Plugin</a>.</p> \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://fontsplugin.com/baskerville-font/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"          \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Google Fonts Similar to Bebas Neue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8: